column1: Table  1.  Gut  contents  of  Notropis  chrosomus  from  Moore  Creek,  Cherokee  County,  GA  by  month.  Numbers  for  each  food  item  indicate  the  total  number  of  in-
dividual  items  of  that  food  type  in  all  guts  examined;  detritus  and  unidentifed  insect  parts  are  exceptions  due  to  the  dificulty  quantifying  them  and  are  noted  by
occurrence  within  a  single  specimen  (e.g.,  the  occurrence  of  detritus  in  two  specimens  from  a  month  is  denoted  as  "2").
